---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: 'Home', url: '/' },
  { name: 'Service Providers', url: '/for-providers' },
  { name: 'Livestock Facilities', url: '/for-providers/livestock' }
];
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Livestock Facilities on BreederHQ Marketplace"
  description="List your handling alley, working chute, scale, AI/repro space, loading facility, or pasture rental on the BreederHQ Marketplace. $5/month, no commissions."
  breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs}
>
<main>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-yellow-50 to-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🐄</div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-6">Livestock Facilities</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
        Handling and sorting alleys, working chutes, scales, AI and repro spaces, loading facilities, and pasture rental.
        Cattle, goat, sheep, and other livestock producers are searching the BreederHQ Marketplace.
      </p>
      <a href="https://accounts.breederhq.com/register?intent=provider_marketplace" class="bg-yellow-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-yellow-600">
        List Your Livestock Facility
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">What you can list</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-stone-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Handling &amp; Working Areas</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Sorting alleys with working pens</li>
            <li>Working chutes (hydraulic, manual, self-catch)</li>
            <li>Scales for weighing and load-out</li>
            <li>AI and reproductive work spaces</li>
            <li>Loading facilities with ramps</li>
            <li>Show prep areas and clipping bays</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-stone-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Pasture &amp; Land</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Short-term pasture rental for finishing or rotation</li>
            <li>Long-term pasture leases</li>
            <li>Quarantine pens and holding pens</li>
            <li>Trailer parking and water access</li>
            <li>Covered working areas</li>
            <li>Electric access for portable equipment</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-stone-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Why it works for livestock facility owners</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">📍</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Local-first discovery</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Producers search by distance and species. They need a chute or scale within trailer range, not three states away.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🐂</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Species and equipment match</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">List the species you support and the equipment you have. Producers with cattle don't waste your time asking about goat-only setups.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🤝</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Repeat business</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Working facility relationships tend to last. One good fall preg-check appointment leads to spring AI, weaning, and shipping season.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Your listing includes</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-yellow-700 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Subtype, species supported, head capacity, acreage</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-yellow-700 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Chute type, scale, loading ramp, sorting alley, palpation cage</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-yellow-700 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">AI station, RFID reader, ultrasound capability</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-yellow-700 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Trailer access, parking, water access, electric access</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-yellow-700 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Quarantine and holding pens, covered working area</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-yellow-700 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Per-session, per-head, per-day, or per-acre pricing</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-6 text-center">
        Livestock facilities use a contact-to-book workflow: producers send an inquiry, you confirm scheduling and arrange payment directly.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Related Provider Categories</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <a href="/for-providers/caprine-services" class="block bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-stone-200 hover:border-amber-300 hover:shadow-sm transition">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Caprine Services</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Goat-specific service categories: disbudding, hoof, DHIR, appraisal, buck, AI, vet, transport.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/for-providers/equine" class="block bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-stone-200 hover:border-amber-300 hover:shadow-sm transition">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Equine Facilities</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Arenas, round pens, wash racks, and trail access.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/for-providers/transport" class="block bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-stone-200 hover:border-amber-300 hover:shadow-sm transition">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Transport</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Cross-species transport hub.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-900 to-yellow-800">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white"><span class="line-through opacity-60 text-2xl">$5/mo</span> Free during early access</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-yellow-200 mb-3">No commissions. No per-session fees. Cancel anytime.</p>
      <p class="text-lg text-yellow-200 mb-8">Get your handling facility, scale, or pasture in front of producers actively looking in your area.</p>
      <a href="https://accounts.breederhq.com/register?intent=provider_marketplace" class="bg-white text-yellow-800 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-yellow-50">
        List Your Livestock Facility
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
</BaseLayout>
